We had killed both the King and Queen by the time Peritus even showed up. So basically this area was broken by us. We did offer to let Peritus loot the 2nd King scroll, which is about the time they showed up. They said no. <br>
<br>
The King and Queen do drop more then the Cleric and Warrior epic pieces. They also drop some pretty good gear. So secondary to the scroll for the cleric, its always nice to pick up a couple Bp's for the warriors and sk's. Along with some pretty nice 2hs weapons for the Sk's and Pally's. When you invest the time and resources necessary to do the Royals, you need some rewards for others.<br>
<br>
